[30;1m97 | [0m[35mrithm for choosing the initial centers for algorithms like K-Means or X-Means.[0m
[30;1m98 | [0m[35m    @details K-Means++ algorithm guarantees an approximation ratio O(log k). Clustering results are [0m
[30;1m99 | [0m[35m              initial centers in case of K-Means algorithm and even in case of X-Means. This method [0m
[30;1m100 | [0m[35m              out optimal initial centers.[0m
[30;1m101 | [0m[35m[0m
